{
  "body": "Please automatically generate a 「museum catalog-style Chinese disassembly infographic」based on【{{subject}}】。\n\nThe entire image is required to combine a realistic main visual, structural disassembly, Chinese annotations, material descriptions, pattern meanings, color meanings, and core feature summaries. You need to automatically determine the most appropriate main subject, clothing system, artifact structure, era style, key components, material craftsmanship, color scheme, and layout structure based on【{{subject}}】, and the user does not need to provide any other information.\n\nThe overall style should be: national museum exhibition boards, historical clothing catalogs, and cultural/museum thematic infographics, rather than ordinary posters, ancient-style portraits, e-commerce detail pages, or anime illustrations. The background uses paper texture: 【{{background_paper}}】, making the overall look premium, restrained, professional, and collectible.\n\n版式固定如下\n- Top: Chinese main title + subtitle + introduction\n- Left: Structural disassembly area, with Chinese lead lines annotating key components, accompanied by close-up details\n- Upper right: Material / craftsmanship / texture area, displaying real texture samples with descriptions\n- Middle right: Pattern / color / meaning area, displaying the main color palette, pattern samples, and cultural explanations\n- Bottom: Dressing order / composition flowchart + core feature summary\n\n本次主题：【{{subject}}】，类型：【{{subject_type}}】。\n\n中央主体处理（依类型自动选择）\n- 若主题适合人物展示（如汉服 / 朝服 / 甲胄），用真人全身正面立姿作为中央主体；\n- 若更适合单体器物或结构展示，则改为中央主体拆解图；\n- 但整体形式仍保持完整的中式信息图。\n\n重点拆解维度（必须出现在画面中，每条以 1–3 行短说明展开）：\n{{highlight_aspects}}\n\n排版与字体\n- All text must be in Simplified Chinese, clear, neat, and readable, without garbled characters, typos, English (except 学名 / 朝代英译可少量出现), or pinyin.\n- 中文标题用稳重宋体或楷书，正文用现代无衬线，关键词可加印章式红框 / 浅色高亮。\n- 引线（lead lines）必须细而清晰，不可压住主体，标注文字小但可读。\n- 模块之间用细线 + 留白分隔，不用厚边框、不用色块铺底。\n\nFocus on highlighting real structures, material differences, cultural explanations, and a catalog atmosphere.\n\n严格规避\nAvoid: poster feel, studio portrait feel, e-commerce feel, anime feel, cosplay feel, random annotations, incorrect structures, blurry text, fake materials, excessive decoration. 不要做成 PPT 板报感，不要做成淘宝详情页，不要塞满促销文案，不要把人物画成网红脸，不要把文物画成游戏建模感。\n\n输出：2:3 竖版，可用于博物馆展板、文化类公众号封面、知识区博主收藏卡。\n\n——————\n主题：{{subject}}\n类型：{{subject_type}}\n背景纸：{{background_paper}}\n拆解维度：{{highlight_aspects}}\n",
